n log your time once you have signed in via Aloha</div><div style="font-family: Times; font-size: medium;"><font face="SalesforceSans, ProximaNovaRegular, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#333333"><span style="background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);">https://foundation.my.salesforce.com/apex/Volunteerforce1?sfdc.tabName=01r80000000Gzb4#/log-hours?log-step=3</span></font></div><br><br>Best wishes, <br><br>Code Club Aotearoa<br></div>]]></td>
